description: Ladies and gents, Janice Dickinson. This week we're talking about the first, maybe the only supermodel to have ever existed. Janice Dickinson's memoir serves us the sauce we've always dreamt of and we love her for it.Follow us on Twitter @cmbc_podcast and Instagram @celebritymemoirbookclub If you want even more juice subscribe to our patreon!!!
